<section id="tools_progress_view">
	<title>Progress view</title>
	<para>Long-running operations, especially every access to directories, 
		are executed in background. The Progress view shows such pending
		operations.
	</para>
	<para>
		<screenshot>
			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata
						fileref="images/tools_progress_view_1.png" format="PNG" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</screenshot>
	</para>	
	<para>
		To cancel a long-running operation press the stop button.
	</para>

</section>